00:06.607 --> 00:08.308 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Judy Woodruff is away.

00:08.342 --> 00:11.778 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight:
President-elect
Donald Trump denies reports of a
disorderly

00:11.812 --> 00:15.916 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
transition as he begins shaping
his new administration.

00:15.949 --> 00:20.721 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Also ahead this Wednesday: As
protests against
the Dakota Access pipeline grow
nationwide,

00:20.754 --> 00:23.790 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
