company trying
to move the oil.

00:23.824 --> 00:26.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KELCY WARREN, CEO, Energy
Transfer Partners:
We're complying with all the
laws, all the

00:26.860 --> 00:29.263 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
rules, and we're overdesigning.

00:29.296 --> 00:34.201 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This pipeline is being built to
safety standards
that far exceed what the
government requires

00:34.234 --> 00:36.036 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
us to do.

