HARI SREENIVASAN: And we head to
the front
lines in the battle against
ISIS, where Iraqi

00:38.906 --> 00:41.842 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
forces try to take back the key
city of Mosul.

00:41.875 --> 00:47.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: This is as far as
the front
line comes here in Mosul in this
neighborhood,

00:47.281 --> 00:50.350 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
