crews trying
to douse flames in seven states
across the

05:23.223 --> 05:25.125 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
South.

05:25.158 --> 05:29.729 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Wildfires have burned roughly
128,000 acres
in woodland areas, much of that
in North Carolina,

05:29.763 --> 05:31.298 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
