conditions.

05:31.331 --> 05:34.668 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
More than 5,000 firefighters are
on the job.

05:34.701 --> 05:39.372 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Officials say heavy smoke from
the fires is
causing breathing problems in a
number of

05:39.406 --> 05:41.308 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
communities.

05:41.341 --> 05:45.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On Wall Street, bank shares gave
up some post-election
gains, and stocks finished
mostly lower.

05:45.278 --> 05:49.416 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
