06:01.494 --> 06:06.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The list includes
singer-songwriter Bruce
Springsteen, actor Tom Hanks,
basketball great

06:06.566 --> 06:11.204 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Michael Jordan, and
mathematician and computer
scientist Margaret Hamilton,
among others.

06:11.238 --> 06:15.642 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They will be recognized in a
White House ceremony
on Tuesday.

