Still to come on the "NewsHour":
potential
conflicts of interest between
the president-elect

06:19.813 --> 06:24.818 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and his business ventures; the
CEO of the
controversial Dakota Access
pipeline on the

06:24.851 --> 06:34.894 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
