for these
jobs, and the reaction from
allies and others

07:05.125 --> 07:08.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
overseas, I'm joined now by
"NewsHour" chief
foreign affairs correspondent
Margaret Warner.

07:08.995 --> 07:14.934 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
