who don't
share the same views.

07:58.912 --> 08:02.349 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Some don't share the views that
Trump enunciated
during the campaign.

08:02.382 --> 08:08.621 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, the people close to the
Trump Organization
say, look, we honestly didn't
expect to win.

08:08.655 --> 08:12.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
