adviser in charge
of this particular part of the
transition.

08:17.430 --> 08:21.468 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I think it is also keeping
with the way
he ran his campaign, which was
kind of freeform

08:21.501 --> 08:23.670 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
