-- or, I
would say, diverse Republican
coalition.

08:35.048 --> 08:39.252 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So, you have John McCain
lecturing him yesterday
about don't get too close to
Putin.

08:39.285 --> 08:46.192 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You have Senator Rand Paul
shooting bullets
at both Bolton and Giuliani,
saying we don't

08:46.226 --> 08:49.162 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
need a hothead in these jobs.

08:49.195 --> 08:56.803 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I think that everybody will
settle down
once you have got these top jobs
filled.

08:56.836 --> 09:03.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Meanwhile,
President Obama
overseas trying to reassure the
E.U., different

09:03.143 --> 09:06.346 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
