47:53.337 --> 47:55.940 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Uterine cancer is very tightly
linked to obesity.

47:55.973 --> 48:01.278 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So, as we see an obesity
epidemic, we're seeing
more and more younger women,
women in their

48:01.312 --> 48:04.181 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
