it requires
-- it requires resources.

48:51.929 --> 48:55.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It requires women to be open to
clinical trials.

48:55.866 --> 49:01.272 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I really want to stress
that, because
